Speaker: Sebastian Neubauer Track:PyConDE Local development of python code inside a docker container is surprisingly broken. In this talk I will walk you through the proper setup of a local python development environment using docker. Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2019 conference. https://pycon.de More details at the conference page: https://de.pycon.org/program/A7FWAW Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
